{"TopicId":175833,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"Dust storm on Mars is threatening the Opportunity rover.","CreatedByName":"Scotius","CreatedById":57622,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-11T22:19:56Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Scotius","CreatedById":57622,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-11T22:19:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBad weather on Mars, folks - and plucky little Opportunity is caught right in the middle of a very, very nasty dust storm. Will its batteries hold out long enough to survive this predicament? Will rover\u0027s solar panels continue to work when sand settles on them? Scott Manley did\u00A0 video on this topic:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/X__AKRqlK4s?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mitchz95","CreatedById":82292,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-12T00:15:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022opportunity.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022278\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/opportunity.png\u0022 width=\u0022740\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOpportunity will be fine. Unfortunately for us.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-12T05:12:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFuture Mars colonists\u00A0emblem.\u003Cbr\u003E\nCrossed geological hammer and pp duster.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022hot-sale-pp-duster-with-cheap-price.jpg